{"word":"G3403 - μιμνήσκω - mimnḗskō - mim-nace'-ko - Be mindful","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μιμνήσκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>mimnḗskō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>mim-nace'-ko"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be mindful"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நினை, நினைத்துக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to remind"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A prolonged form of <a href=\"#/G3415 - μνάομαι - mnáomai - mnah'-om-ahee/3415\">G3415</a> (from which some of the tenses are borrowed); to <i>remind</i>, that is, (middle voice) to <i>recall to mind:</i> - be mindful, remember."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3403 - μιμνήσκω - mimnḗskō - mim-nace'-ko/3403\">G3403</a>, <a href=\"#/G3417 - μνεία - mneía - mni'-ah/3417\">G3417</a>, <a href=\"#/G3418 - μνῆμα - mnēma - mnay'-mah/3418\">G3418</a>, <a href=\"#/G3419 - μνημεῖον - mnēmeîon - mnay-mi'-on/3419\">G3419</a>, <a href=\"#/G3420 - μνήμη - mnḗmē - mnay'-may/3420\">G3420</a>, <a href=\"#/G3421 - μνημονεύω - mnēmoneúō - mnay-mon-yoo'-o/3421\">G3421</a>, <a href=\"#/G3422 - μνημόσυνον - mnēmósynon - mnay-mos'-oo-non/3422\">G3422</a>"}]}